# DX All Suite

This is the top-level DEEPX All Suite repository.

## Submodule Routing

- **dx_app code** (standalone inference): See `dx-runtime/dx_app/.cursor/rules/`
- **dx_stream code** (GStreamer pipelines): See `dx-runtime/dx_stream/.cursor/rules/`
- **Cross-project integration**: See `dx-runtime/.cursor/rules/`

## Conventions

1. Each submodule is self-contained with its own `.deepx/` knowledge base
2. Logging: `logging.getLogger(__name__)` — never bare `print()`
3. NPU check: `dxrt-cli -s` before any NPU operation
4. Always use absolute imports within each submodule

## Process Skills (available at every level)
| Skill | When to use | Read |
|---|---|---|
| Brainstorm & Plan | Before any code generation | Use submodule's `.deepx/skills/dx-brainstorm-and-plan.md` |
| TDD | Validate each file after creation | Use submodule's `.deepx/skills/dx-tdd.md` |
| Verify Completion | Before claiming task is done | Use submodule's `.deepx/skills/dx-verify-completion.md` |

## Interactive Workflow (MUST FOLLOW)
- Ask 2-3 questions before building
- Present plan, get approval
- Validate after generation
- Output to `dx-agentic-dev/<session_id>/` by default

## Session Sentinels (MANDATORY for Automated Testing)

When processing a user prompt, output these exact markers:
- **First line of response**: `[DX-AGENTIC-DEV: START]`
- **Last line after ALL work complete**: `[DX-AGENTIC-DEV: DONE]`
- Sub-agents invoked via routing do NOT output sentinels
- Before DONE: verify all mandatory deliverables exist; create any missing ones
- Before DONE line: output `To save this session as HTML, type: /share html` (Copilot CLI only)
